/*
 * ==================================================================================
 * Feather M0 Low-Power Remote Weather Station Array with Notecard Modem
 * Sensors: SHT31, ICP10111 (Pressure/Temp), SEN0575 Rain Gauge, RS485 Solar
 * I2C (SHT31/ICP/Rain): via DFRobot Gravity TCA9548A I2C Multiplexer (addr 0x70)
 *   on the Feather's main I2C bus — CH0=SHT31, CH1=ICP10111, CH2=Rain gauge
 * Storage: SanDisk Ultra 32GB MicroSD on Adalogger Hardware (Pin 4)
 * Modem: Blues Wireless Notecard (I2C Mode) with ATTN wired to Feather EN Pin
 * RS485 Solar: Software SERCOM1 UART on pins 10 (RX) / 11 (TX)
 * Execution: 10-Minute Power-Gated Wake Cycles / 60-Minute Notehub Sync Window
 * ==================================================================================
 */

